<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Contacto — SenseBagPack</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after {
  margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box;
}

:root {
  --bg:        #faf5f0;
  --navy:      #1e3048;
  --navy-mid:  #253d58;
  --coral:     #c4715a;
  --coral-hi:  #d4856e;
  --coral-dim: rgba(196,113,90,.11);
  --cream:     #faf5f0;
  --sand:      #f0e8e0;
  --white:     #ffffff;
  --border:    #e4dbd2;
  --text:      #1a1f2e;
  --text-mid:  #4a4540;
  --muted:     #9a8c84;
  --green:     #25D366;
}

body {
  min-height: 100vh;
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
}

/* subtle dot texture */
body::before {
  content: '';
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(196,113,90,.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 32px 32px;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 0;
}

/* ─── HEADER ─── */
header {
  background: var(--navy);
  padding: 0 36px;
  height: 66px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.15);
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 100;
}

header::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 2px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--coral), transparent);
  opacity: .5;
}

header h2 {
  font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
  font-size: 1.35rem;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--white);
  letter-spacing: .2px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
}

header h2::before {
  content: '';
  width: 8px; height: 8px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--coral);
  display: inline-block;
  animation: blink 2s ease-in-out infinite;
}

@keyframes blink { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:.25} }

/* ─── MENU ─── */
.menu-container { position: relative; }

.menu-btn {
  width: 38px; height: 38px;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center; align-items: center;
  gap: 5px;
  cursor: pointer;
  border-radius: 9px;
  transition: background .2s;
  padding: 7px;
}

.menu-btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,.1); }

.menu-btn .bar {
  width: 20px; height: 2px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,.8);
  border-radius: 2px;
  transition: all .22s;
}

.menu-btn .bar:nth-child(2) { width: 14px; align-self: flex-end; }

.menu {
  display: none;
  position: absolute;
  right: 0; top: calc(100% + 10px);
  width: 210px;
  background: var(--white);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 16px;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,.13);
}

.menu::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: -6px; right: 14px;
  width: 12px; height: 12px;
  background: var(--white);
  border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  transform: rotate(45deg);
}

.menu a {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  padding: 13px 18px;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: var(--text-mid);
  font-size: .88rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  transition: all .2s;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #f5f0eb;
}

.menu a:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

.menu a .dot {
  width: 6px; height: 6px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--border);
  flex-shrink: 0;
  transition: background .2s;
}

.menu a:hover { background: #fdf4ef; color: var(--coral); padding-left: 22px; }
.menu a:hover .dot { background: var(--coral); }

/* ─── CONTAINER ─── */
.container {
  max-width: 780px;
  margin: 70px auto 60px;
  background: var(--white);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 28px;
  padding: 70px 60px;
  text-align: center;
  box-shadow: 0 16px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.07);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  z-index: 1;
}

/* decorative blobs */
.container::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: -90px; right: -90px;
  width: 300px; height: 300px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(196,113,90,.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
}

.container::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -70px; left: -70px;
  width: 250px; height: 250px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(30,48,72,.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
}

/* eyebrow */
.eyebrow {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 7px;
  background: var(--coral-dim);
  color: var(--coral);
  font-size: .72rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 5px 13px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(196,113,90,.2);
}

.eyebrow-dot {
  width: 5px; height: 5px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--coral);
  animation: blink 2s ease-in-out infinite;
}

h1 {
  font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
  font-size: 2.6rem;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--text);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  line-height: 1.2;
  letter-spacing: -.3px;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

h1 em {
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--coral);
}

p {
  color: var(--muted);
  line-height: 1.85;
  margin-bottom: 36px;
  font-size: 1rem;
  max-width: 560px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  font-weight: 400;
}

/* highlight strip inside p */
.highlight {
  display: inline;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 60%, rgba(196,113,90,.18) 60%);
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--text-mid);
}

/* ─── BUTTONS ─── */
.btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 9px;
  text-decoration: none;
  padding: 14px 28px;
  border-radius: 14px;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: .92rem;
  font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
  transition: all .22s;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  letter-spacing: .2px;
}

.btn i { font-size: 1.1rem; }

.btn-wsp {
  background: var(--green);
  color: white;
  box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(37,211,102,.28);
}

.btn-wsp:hover {
  background: #1ebe5a;
  transform: translateY(-3px);
  box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(37,211,102,.36);
}

.btn-inicio {
  background: var(--coral);
  color: white;
  box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(196,113,90,.28);
}

.btn-inicio:hover {
  background: #b5624c;
  transform: translateY(-3px);
  box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(196,113,90,.36);
}

/* info chips below button */
.info-chips {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 12px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-top: 36px;
  padding-top: 32px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.chip {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 7px;
  background: var(--cream);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  color: var(--text-mid);
  font-size: .78rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  padding: 7px 14px;
  border-radius: 20px;
}

.chip i { font-size: .85rem; color: var(--coral); }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h2>SenseBagPack</h2>
  <div class="menu-container">
    <div class="menu-btn" onclick="toggleMenu()">
      <div class="bar"></div>
      <div class="bar"></div>
      <div class="bar"></div>
    </div>
    <div id="menu" class="menu">
      <a href="/Sensebagpack/vistas/index.jsp"><span class="dot"></span>Inicio</a>
      <a href="/Sensebagpack/vistas/usuario.jsp"><span class="dot"></span>Acceder</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="container">

  <div class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow-dot"></span> Estamos para ayudarte</div>

  <h1>Escribinos <em>ahora</em></h1>

  <p>
    En SensePad llevamos más de un año desarrollando, diseñando y perfeccionando una solución pensada para mejorar la <span class="highlight">autonomía y seguridad</span> de las personas con discapacidad visual. Nuestro compromiso es combinar innovación, accesibilidad y tecnología para brindar mayor tranquilidad tanto a los usuarios como a sus familias.
  </p>

  <a href="https://wa.me/541130091513" target="_blank" class="btn btn-wsp">
    <i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp"></i> Hablanos por WhatsApp
  </a>

  <div class="info-chips">
    <div class="chip"><i class="fa-regular fa-clock"></i> Respondemos en minutos</div>
    <div class="chip"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i> Información confidencial</div>
    <div class="chip"><i class="fa-solid fa-heart"></i> Atención personalizada</div>
  </div>

</div>

<script>
function toggleMenu() {
  const menu = document.getElementById("menu");
  menu.style.display = (menu.style.display === "block") ? "none" : "block";
}
window.onclick = function(event) {
  if (!event.target.closest('.menu-container')) {
    const menu = document.getElementById("menu");
    if (menu.style.display === "block") menu.style.display = "none";
  }
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
